### Wayle Configuration - IWD (WiFi) Module

## IWD Module Configuration

settings-modules-iwd-wifi-disabled-icon = WiFi Disabled Icon
    .description = Icon when WiFi is disabled

settings-modules-iwd-wifi-acquiring-icon = WiFi Connecting Icon
    .description = Icon when WiFi is connecting

settings-modules-iwd-wifi-offline-icon = WiFi Offline Icon
    .description = Icon when WiFi is disconnected

settings-modules-iwd-wifi-connected-icon = WiFi Connected Icon
    .description = Icon when connected but signal strength unavailable

settings-modules-iwd-wifi-signal-icons = Signal Icons
    .description = Icons shown at different WiFi signal strengths, from weak to strong

settings-modules-iwd-border-show = Show Border
    .description = Display border around button

settings-modules-iwd-border-color = Border Color
    .description = Border color token

settings-modules-iwd-icon-show = Show Icon
    .description = Display module icon

settings-modules-iwd-icon-color = Icon Color
    .description = Icon foreground color

settings-modules-iwd-icon-bg-color = Icon Background
    .description = Icon container background color

settings-modules-iwd-label-show = Show Label
    .description = Display connection label

settings-modules-iwd-label-color = Label Color
    .description = Label text color

settings-modules-iwd-label-max-length = Label Max Length
    .description = Max characters before truncation

settings-modules-iwd-button-bg-color = Button Background
    .description = Button background color

settings-modules-iwd-left-click = Left Click
    .description = Shell command on left click

settings-modules-iwd-right-click = Right Click
    .description = Shell command on right click

settings-modules-iwd-middle-click = Middle Click
    .description = Shell command on middle click

settings-modules-iwd-scroll-up = Scroll Up
    .description = Shell command on scroll up

settings-modules-iwd-scroll-down = Scroll Down
    .description = Shell command on scroll down
